Dialogs.Dialog: Hey... What's your favorite "type"？ I mean, in regards to girls.
My type？ Let me see... She has to be...
Kind and obedient, huh？ Hmm, I see.
I thought I have been kind to you lately.
No... Being kind is quite difficult.
Cheerful and positive... I see. Huh...
Eh？ Did I say something weird？
Why？ You're just fond of cheerful and positive girls.
She has to be like ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I really mean it. ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is cool and caring. I really like you.
Eh？ Did I say something weird？
Hey, can I ask what type of girl you like？
Well, sure. For me, she has to be...
Well, kind of... And like... intelligent and mysterious.
I see... I also think that kind of girl is wonderful, but...
I just can't act coldly toward you. Because for me, you are...
No. I got it. I'll try my best！
She has to be just like ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Hey... It was a serious question.
I answered it seriously. You are easy to talk to, and I feel at ease when we're together.
Hey. Has your favorite type changed since the last time I asked？
Huh？ Did I say something weird？
That's not the case, but because you... That's why I...
Geez... Why did it turn out like this？
Actually... It has to be someone just like ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey... Don't try to flatter me.
Hehe. Then, I guess I'll try a bit harder. Yeah...
(I definitely like ▲高嶺＊＊▲ as she is now.)
Um, shall we walk home together？ Maybe we can stop somewhere on the way home too...
Ah, it's from my parents. Excuse me.
I'm sorry. I'm together with a friend from school. I'll be home a little late...
No！ We are not like that yet！ Ah...
Please don't tease me anymore. I'll be home soon.
Sorry. I was asked to be home early today.
Then we won't take any detours. We'll just head straight home together.
You seemed to be flustered with that phone call earlier.
That was... because Mama said something weird...
It's nothing. Um, it was because I told her I was going home with a friend, so she was surprised.
We didn't have time to stop anywhere today, but maybe next time, okay？
Okay. And Mama even gave me her support on that...
No, never mind. See you later.
(I'm kind of curious so maybe I'll take a peek.)
What's up？ Why are you here alone practicing this late？
I'm frustrated that we lost in the doubles match...
Doubles match？ The one we teamed up for？ As I said before, the reason we lost was because I played badly...
No, even if you say so, it was me...
I'm not confident when I play doubles, so I have to practice for the next match.
Of course. I put in so much effort and still lost last time. So now I have to try even harder.
I see. Then how about we practice together？
I have to practice harder too, so that I won't hold you back next time.
Hah. For some reason, I feel good. It was a great practice.
Yes, you've improved a lot. You looked wonderful...
Ah... I mean your tennis！ Like your form when you played... Just the form, okay？
We'll win next time！ Let's show everyone our teamwork！
When I'm with you, I really feel like I can accomplish anything.
Never mind... Thank you for practicing with me. See you later.
(I'd better hurry home and change my outfit...)
"I have something I want to give you. Can you meet me at the school gate？ - Manaka."
(What can it be...？ I'll just hurry over.)
(Why did I have to run errands for Suzuki-sensei on today of all days...？)
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ must have been waiting for me...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, sorry！ Have you been waiting long？
It's okay. I was the one asking you to come here.
I'm sorry. Then what did you want to give me？
Some sweets I made. Think of it as a thank you gift for taking care of me during the doubles match...
Really？ Thanks. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you are so kind.
That's... Um, can you keep this a secret from the others？ I didn't make it for anyone else, only you.
I see, but I will feel bad having this all to myself.
No, it was all because of you that I'm now friends with everyone.
I didn't do anything at all. It was because you tried your best, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, can I open it now？
No means no, so please don't open it until you get home.
Is that so？ Well, if you insist...
▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Why don't we walk toget--
Oh, looks yummy. I'll have a taste.
(Wow, delicious. ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is good at cooking.)
What's going on？ Why are you reading a reference book in the clubroom？
Sometimes when I'm talking with everyone, they ask me questions. That's why I want to be well prepared.
Haha！ So this is ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s secret to making friends, huh？
You know, it's more fun to study in order to be able to answer everyone's questions.
I see... Then studying is something fun for you, huh？
Is it not fun for you？ I'm good at studying, and it feels good to help others. So it's fun.
Did I say something weird again just now？
Not at all. I was just thinking that I could use your help too.
(We are reading this reference book at the same time, so...
(It's natural that we're close to each other...)
(When I look at her like this...)
So, it's like this. Got it？
(I didn't listen to a single word she said... ▲高嶺＊＊▲ didn't catch on...)
Um, this is really embarrassing, isn't it？
No, it's nothing. I'll get going now！
(To think that ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is this defenseless right now...)
(What if I suddenly shout out in a loud voice...)
All right, I'll scare her a little bit...
You got me... Geez, you knew my plan.
You saw my sleeping face, so it's payback... Is it not okay？
...I get it. Sure, it's all right.
I've been staying up late. I've had many things to think about lately.
Are you worried about something？ If I can be of any help...
Thanks. But no, it's something I can't talk to you about.
There's no need for you to fret over it.
Eh？ Well, don't push yourself too hard.
Okay. Ah, it's already this late？ It looks like I had quite a long nap.
Something like that. How about you？
It's fine. I can fix it myself...
Er, huh？ How should I do this？
I have to go, so I'll see you later.
(My heart was racing... Was ▲高嶺＊＊▲ that daring before？)
When you're done over there, I want you to do the other side.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. It is rare bumping into you here.
That's true. I come here occasionally, but I've hardly ever seen you.
...That girl you were talking to just now. She's cute, isn't she？
...That girl. She has been looking this way for a while.
Why don't you at least wave to her？
...▲高嶺＊＊▲. You're not angry, are you？
Not much work to do today...
Don't disturb me when I'm reading.
I saw a friend. I'll go and say hi to her for a bit.
What's up, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ If you're looking for something, I can help. I'm a library committee member after all.
It's fine. I can find it myself.
It's no problem. It's part of a committee member's job and I'm free now.
That's not true. Rather, it seems like I'm the nuisance here...
Never mind. I'm going to look for the book.
▲小早川＊▲. Are you out for a walk？ Looks like you have some free time.
The one with too much free time is you, isn't it？
We've wasted enough time chitchatting. I'm leaving.
That girl just now... Were you on a date or something？
No, no. She's a fellow library committee member. I just ran into her.
But, you two seemed pretty close.
Well, I guess we do get along.
That's true. You seemed to be very well-matched.
(Eh？ What am I supposed to do with this...？)
(Hm, it'll be easier if I just ask ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.)
Okay, I'll take care of that. In exchange, can you handle the sweeping？
▲高嶺＊＊▲？ You were here？ I didn't notice.
Well, I was just passing by and you were in the middle of a conversation.
That person just now is our upperclassman, right？ She's very pretty.
Hm？ Well, I guess so. She's like my supervisor.
No. Sorry for bothering you during work. Do your best.
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ Why was Takane so concerned about Nene-san？)
What am I going to eat today...？
I'm sorry. I was looking away, so...
Hehe. I was wondering whether you would bump into me, so I did it on purpose.
I was just teasing you. Don't be absent-minded, okay？
Well, what am I going to eat...？
What's with me？ I keep bumping into people.
Because you seem to enjoy bumping into people.
You're attending club activities today？ If you're taking a break, do you want to chat a bit？
Hehe... I should get going. Do your best.
Um, I just wanted to talk to you...
You could've just called out to me.
But you were talking with that upperclassman. So I didn't want to interrupt.
You didn't have to worry about that.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. It's unusual to see you here.
No, with Papa and Mama. We're about to leave though.
But then I saw you coming out, so I...
ehe. You need to be mindful of your appearance when going out to service the customers, okay？
I got it. I'll be careful.
Even now, I still have ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ looking after me...
Are you having fun at work？
Well, I guess. It's challenging servicing the customers, but the pay is nice.
You get to work with that pretty upperclassman, too.
Umm, there's something I want to tell you.
Because of you, I've learned to enjoy my life. Is it all right if I consider you my friend？
Thank you. From now on, we'll be good friends, okay？
If I'm good enough to be your friend...
You are. Well, see you later.
(Friends, huh？ If I had pushed myself harder, could we have been more than friends by now...？)
It's not that you are not good or anything, but...
It's because of you that I've made so many friends... The truth is...
No, never mind. It doesn't matter anymore. Goodbye.
